{"tid":178431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚全能既連登仔] 如何對付飛滋","createTime":"2017-03-29T14:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T02:34:05.000Z","uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64837491a254e5a0a86d76a3f1ac15bd22712837","tid":178431,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"生左粒死人飛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食野又痛 笑又痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家野都唔想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇話食維他命C可以快啲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係食左幾舊奇異果都唔見有好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟全能連登仔有冇方法可以對付呢個頑強既敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又有冇咩方法預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生飛滋真係仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7d04c403dcf2b4168c5921dee9b13f1a345921","tid":178431,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d82cd78a38223da3f108ccb228ac62107ce1ef9","tid":178431,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:10:05.000Z","msg":"我bio 呀sir 話用粒有維他命C嘅喉糖壓着粒飛滋"},{"pid":"461ec55741d15457ddaf35b0354ce3ea6fef23a1","tid":178431,"uid":51397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97817a837742e5e1acad50fd97d5b96f3231711","tid":178431,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我bio 呀sir 話用粒有維他命C嘅喉糖壓着粒飛滋</blockquote><br />\n真係有用？