\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889aada51f9634e7b8c974ecfc017d22b057c8ca","tid":178431,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"漱口水"},{"pid":"ffc0229eb9d645ceed09fb064f19e48a097608f5","tid":178431,"uid":91829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用開粗鹽直接撒係飛滋上<br />\n<br />\n好快消炎</blockquote><br />\n消完炎但係都唔識好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果用鹽消完炎再含維他命c糖唔知work唔work呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用鹽就得啦<br />\n無手尾跟"},{"pid":"7bc8aabd0a60a186d661ff80ab448f4f7f1d40a0","tid":178431,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我bio 呀sir 話用粒有維他命C嘅喉糖壓着粒飛滋</blockquote><br />\n真係有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話維他命C用嚟修補啲細胞組織。我試過OK ,不過唔知係咪心理作用。"},{"pid":"a45b727797a2ab35f884d247403530ef3826cf01","tid":178431,"uid":91829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用開粗鹽直接撒係飛滋上<br />\n<br />\n好快消炎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅work<br />\n痛到喊但好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用鹽會搞到嘴唇好腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔見佢消左炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有無用鹽捽爆粒膿？<br />\n要捽爛先有用"},{"pid":"5d806b3f3b6b676cc768e147dc00261c36649a65","tid":178431,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用開粗鹽直接撒係飛滋上<br />\n<br />\n好快消炎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅work<br />\n痛到喊但好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用鹽會搞到嘴唇好腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔見佢消左炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有無用鹽捽爆粒膿？<br />\n要捽爛先有用</blockquote><br />\n諗倒都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n粒鹽要擺成個飛滋定係擺一粒鹽係上面就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要擺幾多日"},{"pid":"1f617a4cbdce1f1880414389dcc21a6bb97ca380","tid":178431,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ipress.com.hk/photo/29441_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipress.com.hk%2Fphoto%2F29441_1.jpg&h=ea9c7ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚正"},{"pid":"475421eee8d209890e4facf290f23e38c0ca0996","tid":178431,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.ipress.com.hk/photo/29441_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipress.com.hk%2Fphoto%2F29441_1.jpg&h=ea9c7ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚正</blockquote><br />\n睇落唔錯😍 有冇效"},{"pid":"b223e7e1f1ce8cbf02f9d0dd23f81a3e906e36e0","tid":178431,"uid":26090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T20:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.ipress.com.hk/photo/29441_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipress.com.hk%2Fphoto%2F29441_1.jpg&h=ea9c7ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚正</blockquote><br />\n睇落唔錯😍 有冇效</blockquote><br />\n我用過 嗽完水後 仲會好&quot;哪&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用維他命C片（唔係沖水飲個隻）攝去飛滋位。<br />\n一兩次就冇咁痛 仲好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46824772a685ea2923138d16a5737246737cac5","tid":178431,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T20:41:54.000Z","msg":"睇錯愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee389a1461fde1c46265d2ae52b1f4a911b12564","tid":178431,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.ipress.com.hk/photo/29441_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipress.com.hk%2Fphoto%2F29441_1.jpg&h=ea9c7ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚正</blockquote><br />\n睇落唔錯😍 有冇效</blockquote><br />\n有 用完之後一啲都唔痛<br />\n果種感覺好奇妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41c5b777c8337bda493f1b7f32d192507d8544e","tid":178431,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:18:31.000Z","msg":"預防勝於治療 <br />\n你唔夠維他命b群 試下日日飲紅豆之後會生少好多<br />\n我之前都試過一之過生七粒 唔好再信啲熱咩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：食完紅豆半年冇生過"},{"pid":"bca9e1a7ad8daf3e4f2c22054a70a44797646dfc","tid":178431,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:19:01.000Z","msg":"之前用過隻飛滋貼 ㄧ晚就好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泡菜國出"},{"pid":"20d3262dbca8a5d53ada040b45b4b3edf3ca0ad7","tid":178431,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:23:40.000Z","msg":"好返之後Keep住每日食維他命B雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：食咗半年有多無再生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adf42c7742488de2e332d4f6aafb5b7817c74d2","tid":178431,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:28:29.000Z","msg":"用濃鹽水漱口<br />\n利申家姐讀醫<br />\n<br />\n不過我自己就用鹽直接乸落去 好有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38051b8af3dd8f960c93571a39b7156009da1107","tid":178431,"uid":36804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.ipress.com.hk/photo/29441_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipress.com.hk%2Fphoto%2F29441_1.jpg&h=ea9c7ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚正</blockquote><br />\n睇落唔錯😍 有冇效</blockquote><br />\n有 用完之後一啲都唔痛<br />\n果種感覺好奇妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只能用一次, 每次30蚊<br />\n<br />\n但真係5秒搞掟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}